VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT UIPasteboard\.general\.(string|setValue|setData|setObjects)\s*[=\(]
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:password|token|secret|key|credential|auth && MISSING:localOnly|expirationDate|UIPasteboardOption
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects writes of sensitive data to the system pasteboard without expiration or local-only restrictions.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for UIPasteboard Write with Sensitive Data.
